subSubSection.paragraph:
Ecology .—Lower intertidal to about 35 m (
Crosnier & Forest 1966
); hard bottoms, in crevices of calcareous algal crusts and overgrown rocks, also in coral rubble and under rocks on mixed sand-rock bottoms.

Distribution .—Eastern Atlantic: Ivory Coast ; Gulf of Guinea : São Tomé and Principe (
Crosnier & Forest 1966
).
